 tau and the spectral index n_s to\nvary. We present a simple demonstration of how the weak lensing results can be\nused as a prior in the parameter estimation from CMB measurements to derive\nconstraints on the reionization optical depth tau. (abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Apr 2002 21:01:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Jun 2002 19:13:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
