cs. The harmonic surfaces in the\nmanifold of spacetimes are expected to have novel nonperturbative effects at\nlarge distances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Apr 2002 19:05:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
