 limit due to the finite correlation time is positive (that is,\nthe anomalous scaling is suppressed), it is maximal for the quenched limit and\nmonotonically decreases as the correlation time tends to zero.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Apr 2002 06:54:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
